Package: LibeRties
Title: Task Infrastructure and Execution Service for LibeRation
Version: 0.4.0
Authors@R:
    person("Sven C.", "van Dijkman", email = "svdijkman@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: LibeRties (Task Infrastructure and Execution Service) provides
    container-sandboxed remote job scheduling for LibeRation with API token
    authentication, per-user resource limits, dataset integrity checks (MD5),
    and an admin Shiny application.
